1. install pipenv
    pip3 install pipenv
2. use python 3 for pipenv
    pipenv --three
3. install flask
    pipenv install flask
4. install translate
    pipenv install translate
5. cd to the folder that contains bootstrap.sh and run the bootstrap
    ./bootstrap.sh
6. use a NEW terminal to fetch the translated data
    a. translate ch to en
        Curl command:
        curl -X GET -H http://localhost:5000/convert_ch_to_en?word=愤怒

        You will get:
        "Rage"
    b. translate en to ch
        Curl command:
        curl -X GET -H http://localhost:5000/convert_en_to_ch?word=happy

        You will get:
        "\u5e78\u798f\u7684"
